{
  "texts": [
    "Currently, there is also no artificial intelligence (AI) system capable of effectively integrating FFA image-text information and providing QA interactions.",
    "To maximize the AI-assisted interpretation of FFA images, our goal is to develop a two-stage FFA-GPT system.",
    "By combining the capabilities of image-text conversion models and LLMs, we aim to achieve FFA report generation and subsequent interactive QA, thereby reducing the reliance on retinal specialists.",
    "The study flow chart is shown in Fig. 1.",
    "The final dataset used in the study consisted of 654,343 FFA images paired with 9392 reports."
  ]
}